mods:titleInfo.mods:title: The Australian Lymexylidae (Coleoptera: Tenerionoidea) with one new genus and two genera new to Australia

paragraph.treatmentCitationGroup:
Hylecoetus fuscipennis Lea, 1912: 466
. Type , ♀ , SAM. Examined by Wheeler (1986) .

subSubSection.paragraph:
Diagnosis .
Australymexylon fuscipennis
differs from
A. australe
in its lighter colour, especially at the elytral bases and males with strongly serrate antenna, smaller setose pads on segment VIII and much smaller penis.
